title: Brooke Shields
itunes:title: Brooke Shields
description:
Brooke Shields [Pretty Baby, The Blue Lagoon, Suddenly Susan, A Castle for Christmas] talks with Anna about first loves, how not to get mugged, motherhood, growing up in the public eye, meeting her husband, and much more.


For our Unqualified segment we catch up with callers from past episodes and find out how they’ve been doing since we had them on the podcast. First up is Jessie whose dream of competing in the Olympics meant having to leave her home and family. Jessie spoke with Anna and April Beyer on the August 23rd 2021 episode with Liz Gillies. We then hear from Kelsey whose unpleasant work environment took a turn for the worse when her promotion led to a jealous co-worker’s attempted sabotage. Kelsey spoke with Anna and Brooke Burke on October 4th 2021.


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
